    Locations

    locations.Rmd

    Setup

    library(googleAuthR)
library(googleCloudAutoMLTablesR)

options(googleAuthR.scopes.selected = "https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform")

gar_auth_service(json_file = Sys.getenv("GAR_SERVICE_JSON"))
    # assumes you have projectId string set to environment argument GCAT_DEFAULT_PROJECT_ID
gcat_region_set("us-central1")
    ## 2020-03-27 11:03:16> Region set to us-central1
    ## [1] "us-central1"
    gcat_project_set(Sys.getenv("GCAT_DEFAULT_PROJECT_ID"))
    ## 2020-03-27 11:03:16> ProjectId set to gc-automl-tables-r
    ## [1] "gc-automl-tables-r"

    Get list of locations

    locations_list <- gcat_list_locations()
locations_list
    ##                                                name  locationId
## 1          projects/gc-automl-tables-r/locations/eu          eu
## 2 projects/gc-automl-tables-r/locations/us-central1 us-central1

    Set location

    location_path <- gcat_get_location()
location_path
    ## ==Google Cloud AutoML Tables Location==
## name:                 projects/gc-automl-tables-r/locations/us-central1 
## locationId:           us-central1
